{"tid":754504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2018 3間發鈔銀行新鈔票","createTime":"2018-07-24T12:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T21:26:14.000Z","uid":195477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4be22f7162a6b2575a5003c03f466914d1c6a001","tid":754504,"uid":195477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/203544_f30a5431c9a1f2887ed0615dcd7b77df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F203544_f30a5431c9a1f2887ed0615dcd7b77df.png&h=1d3c635d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/203553_c65e63d06867adab5fed0bda81de7050.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F203553_c65e63d06867adab5fed0bda81de7050.png&h=1c067349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018 新鈔票與現時市面流通的銀紙一樣，同樣具有 5 個面額，並採用相同的顏色，設計主題富香港特色，當中 1,000 元鈔票就描繪香港作為金融中心的地位、500 元鈔票則是描繪世界地質公園、100 元鈔票則描繪關於藝術的粵劇，而 50 元鈔票為本港棲息的蝴蝶；至於 20 元鈔票則描繪市民大眾最愛的點心及飲茶文化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2122006/2018%20%E6%96%B0%E9%88%94%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%8C%E7%9B%B4%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%8D%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4%EF%BC%813%20%E7%99%BC%E9%88%94%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%A1%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E5%AF%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2122006%2F2018%2520%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2588%2594%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B4%25EF%25BC%25813%2520%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2588%2594%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%258E%25A1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%25AF%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%2589%25B2&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ead92207\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2122006/2018%20%E6%96%B0%E9%88%94%E7%A5%A8%E3%80%8C%E7%9B%B4%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%8D%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4%EF%BC%813%20%E7%99%BC%E9%88%94%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%A1%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E5%AF%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n最鐘意中銀100蚊 就黎七月十四驅鬼一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 點解要「直度」 有人銀包設計係直度架咩？"},{"pid":"337e5524773e5716b3ba05bdd094d01cee042fb5","tid":754504,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"匯豐最正常<br />\n中銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國風"},{"pid":"142e5f67094d8634922772f13230725398662b97","tid":754504,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cbdcae6e8c1ab11da188f1c5edd526b4b4569c","tid":754504,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:26:14.000Z","msg":"以前唔係三間銀行自己一間一個主題㗎咩? 搞乜今次一套主題三間跟?"}]}